Package pacman.guiobjects

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CreationMenu
    This class manages the creationmenu, that allows user to create a new level or modify an old one.
    CreationMode
    Used to create and modify levels.
    FinishCreation
    Menu where user can define the name and timeframe of a level and fill it with pointbubbles.
    Help
    Used to provide the instructionscreen to creationmode.
    Highscores
    Used to show the highscores of a level.
    LevelCompleted
    Menu that will be shown to the player once a level is finished.
    LevelFailed
    Screen that is shown to the player if he/she loses the level.
    LevelSelectionMenu
    Menu that will be shown to the player once he/she has decided to play or modify a level.
    StartMenu
    Menu that will be shown to the user when the program starts.
    StartMenuAnimation
    This class provides the animation for the StartMenu.
